{"tid":311654,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日扮工果陣隔離位同事玩射擊","createTime":"2017-07-06T20:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T04:30:39.000Z","uid":63979,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7c6cae723c23bd1c765a100befa8c63edb171ca","tid":311654,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T20:00:15.000Z","msg":"今日扮工果陣有隻烏蠅係度飛黎飛去，隔離位同事即刻拎條橡根出黎對隻烏蠅進行射擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一擊唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻野繼續飛下飛下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二擊射中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要跌落我張枱度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細心睇隻烏蠅，原來個同事射甩左佢個頭，仲要搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我位同事就搵膠紙痴住隻烏蠅半條屍扔落垃圾筒，之後我地兩個係度搵個烏蠅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細心搵，hi！原來跌左落我個keyboard度，好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我位同事又搵張膠紙痴住個烏蠅頭再扔落垃圾筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗返我位同事真係幾勁，咁到射得中隻烏蠅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77eb4a3feb33343001366b56ee27e82f0aa62c41","tid":311654,"uid":7374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T20:23:43.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"642b4ed5b926f5710804b7ded2cecc3118bbcc4f","tid":311654,"uid":7119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T20:44:10.000Z","msg":"以為想問卷膠紙用哂 邊度買會平啲"},{"pid":"bde1d93a10b821548d0354cc641414f0d024d9c6","tid":311654,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為想問卷膠紙用哂 邊度買會平啲</blockquote><br />\n用晒問公司攞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}